f=Engineering/dev/custom/architecture-decisions/assets/adr-template.md · h1:ADR-[NNN]: [short title decision]=**Status:** [proposed accepted superseded-by ADR-NNN] **Date:** [YYYY-MM-DD] **Deciders:** [dev domain agents/operator] **Supersedes:** [ADR-NNN · h2:Context=[The forces play, honestly. What problem, what constraints (the stack profile, Security Charter, budget, timeline), what's pushing us. State assumptions.] · h2:Options considered=[At least two. each: what is, trade-offs. "We found one option" itself worth recording.] **[Option A]** [pros cons] **[Option B]** [pros cons] **[Option C]** (if any) [pros cons] · h2:Decision=[The option chosen, deciding reason. One paragraph.] · h2:Consequences=**Positive:** [what buys us], **Negative costs:** [what accept downsides, stated plainly], **Follow-ups:** [migrations, ADRs forces later, risks watch] · h2:Domain review=[Which agents reviewed (data/backend/frontend/mobile/security/reliability), any dissent recorded, hidden.] · h2:Charter check=[Confirm decision weaken any Security Charter rail. touches security posture, aegis reviewed.]